<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>القَوْل/ع،<span class="c5"> الْكَلاَم/ع:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">عَرْقَلَ فُلاَنٌ عَلَى فُلاَنٍ الكَلاَمَ أَيْ:</span> خَادَعَهُ فِيهِ وَأَرَادَ إِقْنَاعَهُ بِمَا لاَ يَصِحّ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{لِسَانُ العَرَب: ٤٤٠/ ١١}</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">بَابُ الْكَلاَم:</span> <span class="c4">[انْظُرِ الْقَوْلَ بحَرْفِ الْقَاف]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>بَابُ المَلاَبِسِ/ع، اللِّبَاس/ع، وَالثِّيَاب/ع،<span class="c5"> الثَّوْب/ع:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">التُّبَّان:</span> هُوَ <span class="c1">" السِّلِبّ "</span> أَو <span class="c1">" الكُلُتّ "</span> ٠٠!!<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>نَمِّلْ ثَوْبَكَ أَيِ ارْفَأْهُ ٠ <span class="c3">{لِسَانُ العَرَب: ٦٧٩/ ١١}</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">المَرْأَة:</span> <span class="c4">[انْظُرِ الرَّجُلَ ٠ بحَرْفِ الرَّاء]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>